"8WRGN22U..0A1G" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos. According to the [http://wiki.openwrt.org/toh/d-link/dir-615 OpenWrt wiki], the device has 8MB Flash
(MX29LV640ETBI-70G) and 32MB RAM (2x W9812G6IH). {{seealso|D-Link DIR-615 series}} 

====Revision G1====
Architecture: MIPS
Bootloader: U-Boot
System-On-Chip: Ralink RT3052F
CPU Speed: 384 MHz
Flash-Chip: Macronix MX29LV640ETBI-70G
Flash size: 8 MiB
RAM-Chip: 2x Winbond W9812G6IH
RAM size: 32 MiB (2x 2M x 4 x 16bit)
Wireless: SoC integrated
Ethernet: SoC integrated
USB: Unknown
Serial: Yes
JTAG: Unknown
